---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 color-combo-blue-creme">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-primary-semibold text-scale-3 sm:text-scale-4 text-foreground tracking-tight leading-tight">
          About Pyre
        </h2>
        
        <p class="font-primary-regular text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Pyre is more than just a sauna and cold plunge facility. We're creating a wellness sanctuary where ancient traditions meet modern comfort, designed to nourish your body, mind, and spirit.
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-primary-regular text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Our mission is to provide a welcoming space for the Richmond community to experience the transformative benefits of heat therapy, cold therapy, and mindful wellness practices. Whether you're a wellness enthusiast or just beginning your journey, Pyre offers a sanctuary for all.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="font-primary-semibold text-xl text-foreground">Traditional Wisdom</h3>
            <p class="font-primary-regular text-muted-foreground">
              Rooted in centuries-old practices from Finland and beyond, our saunas and cold therapy facilities honor the traditions that have supported human wellness for generations.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="font-primary-semibold text-xl text-foreground">Modern Comfort</h3>
            <p class="font-primary-regular text-muted-foreground">
              While we honor tradition, we also embrace modern design and amenities to ensure your experience is both authentic and comfortable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pt-6">
          <a 
            href="#signup" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-primary-semibold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Join Our Community
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <Image 
          src="/images/flowers_on_back.jpeg" 
          alt="Wellness and relaxation" 
          class="w-full h-96 lg:h-[500px] object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          width={600}
          height={500}
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background/20 to-transparent rounded-lg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 